modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod utilizes the in-game Developer Rocket [Boots](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-clothing/) but makes them a little more reasonable. You can also craft them. They can also be bought at Traders for a high price and sold, too.

**[Download](https://github.com/GopherMods/7DTDMods/raw/master/RocketBoots.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/17309-gophers-modlets-not-an-all-in-one-pack/).

**Credits:** [Gopher](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/gopher/)
